      "description": "Badang unleashes a gust of (Fist Wind) in the target direction, dealing 125( +90% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to enemies hit, slowing them by 30% for 1.5s, and knocking them back. The (Fist Wind) will explode upon hitting an obstacle, dealing 100( +60% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to nearby enemies. (Fist Wind) can trigger attack effects and grants Badang 1 (Chivalry Fist) stack upon cast. Badang stores up to 2 (Fist Wind) charges and restores 1 charge every 10.4s.",
