      "description": "Badang dashes in the target direction, dealing 230( +50% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to enemies in his path while gaining a 350( +150% Total Physical Attack) shield that lasts 5s. He stops immediately upon hitting an enemy hero, slightly knocking them back while creating an obstacle that lasts 4s behind them. Enemies hit by the obstacle are dealt 130( +30% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage). (Use Again): Badang removes the obstacle he created.",
